=Description=

"When we published the State of Web3 Grants Report last year, we set out on a path to demystify the world of web3 grants. In the process, we uncovered tons of similarities in the types of challenges various operators across the industry were experiencing. We also identified shortcomings and opportunities, especially around reporting, evaluation, and tools that would allow for improved management of programs. In the year since, we’ve observed a shift in grant programs with regards to how they’ve grown and how sophisticated they’ve become. In our 2023 report, we covered 13 programs. In this 2024 version, we’ve
covered 13 programs and 5 tooling companies."

